      <textAnnotation id="sid-E887E019-3BF2-4314-B0B3-315F4FCB41DF" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>AS-IS Process of FA outside SAP

If IFA outcome is negative (meaning product is ok), then reject request offline and communicate to customer.

If FA outcome is positive (Meaning product is not ok), then it will trigger E2E-10  (for FOC or Credit Memo) with no physical receipt based on remedy path.
</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-2349079A-5EC9-4E35-AD9F-65DE4EDAD3AE" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>By Customer Quality Engineer</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-1E2EE4FB-B88F-475A-8221-9BDA3E66EBB4" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Customer Quality Engineer
</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-7720EA13-E9FA-445D-9875-87F0EA5C15DF" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Certificate of destruction recorded by Quality Analyst Manually
</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-32245354-B993-4AF2-86D8-82BC07D1B666" signavio:alignment="left">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioType dataObjectType="IT-System"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bgcolor" metaValue="#e1e1e1"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
            <signavio:signavioLabel bottom="false" left="false" ref="text_name" right="false" top="true" valign="bottom" x="32.0" y="-20.0"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>CIBR</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-478ED613-45E2-4DAF-8E79-03241C94C508" signavio:alignment="left">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioDictionaryLink propertyId="name">
               <signavio:dictionaryLink>/glossary/1c1bc4da26d14a57a1057b1e4f24ae60</signavio:dictionaryLink>
            </signavio:signavioDictionaryLink>
            <signavio:signavioType dataObjectType="IT-System"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bgcolor" metaValue="#e1e1e1"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
            <signavio:signavioLabel bottom="false" left="false" ref="text_name" right="false" top="true" valign="bottom" x="32.0" y="-20.0"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Alfresco Content Management System</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-4378CCDA-F407-4320-95FA-8C3A9D524488" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>With or Without reference to original invoice
</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-700DA984-7D1B-4B61-90D2-6A11ABC3B899" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>SPL
Embargo
</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-990DB70B-477E-4646-AF92-C2B99861D9E3" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Same Batch ID as original / Return order. Serial numbers not captured.
Physical verification - Items Received based on original shipping media (FOSB for wafers/Tape and reels for Die)
</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-20982C7E-A2BF-4EB7-A3D2-92689E2F2C69" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Refer E2E-23 for FOC process
</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-007096D4-C09A-4F74-B897-BB6E5B6D0A29" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Refer E2E-04 for full Credit Memo Steps
</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-7DD3AAAD-BA8D-48FA-B8AC-BBD245047870" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>No Credit provided to Customer, will follow Sales Process, new Sales Engagement with Customer with Service Order
</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-69D57E16-1307-47AB-91CD-A61FFBB7F570" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>MVT Type :  655/657 
Dr: Inventory 
Cr: COGS
</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-5D95B40A-4E8B-4924-94A7-B73C62D7DBB9" signavio:alignment="left">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioType dataObjectType="IT-System"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bgcolor" metaValue="#e1e1e1"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>GTS Trade Compliance</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-352EFA34-570C-488D-AD1B-8B85BCE156A5" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Customer MM 
ID validation order reasons 
</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-E5FBC2CF-9E60-467B-8BB0-948D02BC8989" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>MSR_INSPWH</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-EA1C83C7-50AE-4AAB-815C-03BF8F040B77" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Auto Creation
</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-7D7FCFB1-43D7-4D60-AC4A-A173C26E6630" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>If FA states Product is not OK
And aligned with customer on remedy path
</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-193E48C7-7EC0-4588-B9EF-FDC11A46B863" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Manual Update of Inspection once confirmed
</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-00AD9E53-F697-485C-8475-798577DFA0CD" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Follow up actions – FOC, Credit Memo and Moving items to scrap performed automatically. Further Scrapping to be handled outside SAP as per Process Documentation, and movements recorded manually in SAP.
</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-A45892E6-C5D9-408A-B1BF-BC05503E0603" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Initiate Return to Customer process in-case of discrepant/unacceptable / no remedy / out of warranty product and customer agreed for return instead of waster processing at Intel Site</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-729AC96A-AE4A-41AC-A2E5-DD87DC7E26D7" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>MVT Type :  601
Dr: COGS
Cr: Inventory
</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-10138EE9-28E5-4895-8990-35DE76A0AB1C" signavio:alignment="left">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioType dataObjectType="IT-System"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bgcolor" metaValue="#e1e1e1"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
            <signavio:signavioLabel bottom="false" left="false" ref="text_name" right="false" top="true" valign="bottom" x="32.0" y="-20.0"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>GTS Check</text>
      </textAnnotation>
   </process>
   <process id="sid-7a120959-193f-415f-8aa2-0e6c2b3a4c3c" isClosed="false" isExecutable="false" processType="None">
      <task completionQuantity="1" id="sid-C90879E0-A6F3-4CAF-8C58-C4119ACFDCEA" isForCompensation="false" name="Forecast to Stock" startQuantity="1">
